== Nahum achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Nahum'''

[[File:Prophet Nahum Basilica of St. John Lateran.jpg|thumb|left|Prophet Nahum,  Basilica of St. John Lateran]]
[[File:Nineveh map city walls & gates.JPG|thumb|Nineveh map city walls & gates]]
[[File:The prophet Naum from the shrine of the Three Magi.jpg|thumb|left|The prophet Naum from the shrine of the Three Magi]]

Nahumachem pustok eka stotrantlean suru zata. Hea stotrant, sorvespor noxtteancho sudd gheta ani Assiriek khast lavun Judak taronn dita tem dakhoilam (1/2 – 2/3).  Punn hea pustokacho mathallo zaun asa tacho mukhel vixoi :  NINEVEHCHEM NISONNTON.  Hem Nahum provadi bhakit korun eke kovitentlean sangta ani hea vorvim Israelantlo to ek vhodd kovi mhonn kollun ieta (2/4-3/19).

Nahumachea pustoka vorvim, Israelachea lokancho bhorvanso vaddlach astolo.  Punn hi bhorvanxachi khuxalkai thoddoch kall thogli.   Ninevehchea nisonttona uprant rokddench Jerusaleachem nisontton zalem.  Tea uprant hea sondeshacho khub vistar zata. Izaias provadi (Iz. 52/7) otmik taronn dakhoun, Nahumachea (Na.2/1) bhakitacho upeog korta.


